				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Practical effect of CS3?<a name="54575"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jul 31 04 9:33 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>CS dps mitigation &gt; LR dps mitigation in the LONG RUN.  LR may save more over time, but it only increases 1% avoidance PER RANK.
<br />

<br />
CS may not be as good as CA and ID may not be as good as LR but CS &gt; LR.  The parses for warriors say CS is better and I am making a leap of faith but I assume* that it would be the same for bards.
<br />

<br />
P.S.  Get ND3, PE, CA1, CS1, CA3 :p.  PE is a very nice upgrade / point cost but only works if you have a rank bought in it.</span></td>
